sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User<br/>Mobile Device
    participant SE as Secure Element<br/>or HCE Service
    participant NFC as NFC Controller<br/>13.56 MHz
    participant Terminal as POS Terminal<br/>NFC Reader
    participant Acquirer as Acquirer<br/>Processor
    participant Network as Card Network<br/>VisaNet or Banknet
    participant TSP as TSP<br/>VTS or MDES
    participant Issuer as Issuing<br/>Bank

    Note over User,Issuer: In-Store NFC Transaction -- Detailed Timing

    User->>SE: Authenticate -- biometric<br/>T+0ms
    SE->>SE: Verify Face ID or fingerprint<br/>T+200ms

    NFC->>Terminal: Phone enters RF field<br/>T+200ms
    Terminal->>NFC: SELECT PPSE<br/>T+220ms
    NFC->>SE: Route APDU
    SE-->>NFC: AID list response
    NFC-->>Terminal: Available payment AIDs

    Terminal->>NFC: SELECT AID<br/>T+240ms
    Terminal->>NFC: GET PROCESSING OPTIONS<br/>T+260ms
    NFC->>SE: Forward GPO with amount
    SE-->>NFC: AIP and AFL response

    Terminal->>NFC: READ RECORD<br/>T+280ms
    SE->>SE: Generate cryptogram<br/>ARQC from token key + ATC<br/>T+320ms
    NFC-->>Terminal: DPAN + cryptogram + ATC<br/>T+350ms

    Note over User,Terminal: NFC PHASE COMPLETE -- 350ms

    Terminal->>Acquirer: ISO 8583 MTI 0100<br/>DPAN, amount, cryptogram<br/>T+450ms
    Acquirer->>Network: Route via token BIN range<br/>T+500ms

    Network->>TSP: Detokenize request<br/>T+700ms
    TSP->>TSP: Map DPAN to real FPAN<br/>Validate cryptogram via HSM<br/>Check domain restriction
    TSP-->>Network: Real FPAN + validation result<br/>T+850ms

    Network->>Issuer: Auth request with real PAN<br/>T+900ms
    Issuer->>Issuer: Balance check, fraud scoring<br/>velocity limits<br/>T+1200ms
    Issuer-->>Network: Response code 00 -- Approved<br/>T+1400ms

    Network->>TSP: Re-tokenize response
    TSP-->>Network: Response with DPAN<br/>T+1500ms

    Network-->>Acquirer: Approved<br/>T+1600ms
    Acquirer-->>Terminal: Approved<br/>T+1700ms
    Terminal-->>User: Display approved<br/>Haptic feedback<br/>T+1900ms

    Note over User,Issuer: TOTAL: approximately 2 seconds
